Sheila - As far as proving the money belongs to Credit, have we had anything back from
Goldmans on docs opening a new ECI bank account? From Credit Trading's perspective,
I think we can demonstrate that ENA had no economic interest in this account:

- Credit traders directed all of the trading activity in this account
- all trading positions and P&L were reported in Credit's DPR and in Enron Credit Inc
- all margin requirements were funded from Credit's Citibank account in London

  
Thanks
Simon

